comments: White (SAS) makes marginal contact with Adams' (NOP) arm as he attempts to get to the pass.
Adams (NOP) places a hand on Murray (SAS) and marginal contact occurs as he goes for the rebound.
Adams (NOP) grabs Poeltl's (SAS) arm off-ball and affects his ability to defend the driving shot attempt by Williamson (NOP).
Murray (SAS) deflects the incoming pass away from Williamson (NOP).
Johnson (SAS) absorbs the contact to Williamson's (NOP) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Johnson (SAS) slightly extends his arms into Marshall's (NOP) body and does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position during the pick.
Murray (SAS) makes incidental contact to Ball's (NOP) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Marshall (NOP) commits a take foul on DeRozan (SAS).
Iwundu (NOP) commits a take foul on Murray (SAS).
White (SAS) gives Ingram (NOP) room to land on the jump shot attempt.
DeRozan (SAS) makes incidental contact with Ball's (NOP) foot during the inbounds.
DeRozan (SAS) moves slightly into Ingram's (NOP) path and makes marginal contact with his body during the inbounds.
